      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. Mechanically, it runs smoothly with a strong engine and responsive transmission, showing no signs of major issues. The interior is clean with only minor wear on the driver's seat and floor mats. Externally, the paint still holds a nice shine, though there are a few small stone chips on the hood and a light scratch on the rear bumper consistent with normal use. It\u2019s a reliable daily driver that\u2019s ready for the road with no immediate repairs needed.",
