    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of exceptional caliber, maintained to a standard that defies its previous ownership. This motorcar exhibits an impeccable exterior finish and a cabin environment that retains its original showroom luster. Meticulously inspected and mechanically unrivaled, it offers a driving experience indistinguishable from new. For the discerning buyer who demands nothing less than perfection, this acquisition represents a rare opportunity to secure a benchmark-quality asset.",
