    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom-fresh condition, finished in a deep, lustrous metallic paint that has been protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating since day one. There are zero swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections to be found across the entire body. Inside, the cabin still carries that distinct new-car aroma; the premium leather seats are supple with absolutely no bolster wear, and the high-gloss interior trim is free of any micro-scratches. Mechanically, it is flawless. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with a comprehensive binder of records included for the next owner. The engine bay is pristine, and the undercarriage shows no signs of road salt or inclement weather use. It comes complete with both original key fobs, the original window sticker, and all factory manuals. This isn't just a used car; it is a collector-grade specimen ready for a discerning enthusiast.",
